This modern office facility is located in the Smithfield industrial precinct. The location provides quick and easy access to the Cumberland Highway, The Horsley Drive and the M4 and M7 Motorways.

The modern suite features: 

- Multiple meeting rooms + staff breakout area
- Collaborative open plan work area
- Ample Parking 
- Fantastic natural light
- Available Now

Please contact the exclusive agents if you wish to inspect.

Situated in the Smithfield industrial precinct. Close proximity to the Cumberland Highway, minutes from the Great Western Highway & the M4 Western Motorway. 

- Large industrial warehouse unit with office accomadation
- Clearspan warehouse with an internal clearance of 6m-6.6m (approx)
- Access via one (1) roller shutter door measuring 5m wide x 5.0m high
- Nineteen (19) car parking spaces
- Office accommodation split over two levels 
- Container friendly


Please contact either Janet or Elijah for further information.

Situated in the heart of the Smithfield industrial precinct providing excellent access to main arterial roads such as the M4 & M7 Motorways & The Cumberland Highway.

• Site Area: 10,000sqm*
• Access via (3) on grade roller doors & (1) recessed dock
• High internal clearance of up to 11m*
• Fully sprinklered & racked facility
• Exclusive secure yard area for easy truck access
• Available December 2021
• Carpeted & air-conditioned office with kitchenette & amenities

For further information or to arrange an inspection,
please contact the exclusively listed agents.
